ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectConvention concerning Forced or Compulsory Labour, **RATIFICATION**
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to ratify on behalf of Canada the CONVENTION CONCERNING FORCED OR COMPULSORY LABOUR, adopted at Geneva on 28 June 1930 (as modified by the Final Articles Revision Convention, 1946).
